FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777107988
OL,3,COn the campaign trail with Scotland's
OL,4,Cleaders ahead of crucial elections
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThat makes the SNP's position all the
OL,12,Fmore interesting this time around.
OL,13,FAfter 19 years in power, the polls
OL,14,Fsuggest they are on course to win
OL,15,Fagain, and they are aiming for an
OL,16,Foverall majority.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31719
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777107988
OL,3,COn the campaign trail with Scotland's
OL,4,Cleaders ahead of crucial elections
OL,6,FThat has only happened once before,
OL,7,Funder Alex Salmond in 2011, and it was
OL,8,Ffollowed by an independence
OL,9,Freferendum. The party is running on
OL,10,Fthat principle once again: an SNP
OL,11,Foverall majority in Holyrood, they
OL,12,Fsay, ought to trigger another vote on
OL,13,FScotland's place in the UK.
OL,15,FThe result of this Scottish election
OL,16,Fcould reshape the UK, particularly if
OL,17,Fall three of the devolved nations end
OL,18,Fup being led by 'pro-separation'
OL,19,Fparties on May 8.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
