PN,31720
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777107988
OL,3,COn the campaign trail with Scotland's
OL,4,Cleaders ahead of crucial elections
OL,6,FIf devolution is designed to give the
OL,7,Fpeople of those nations a voice, that
OL,8,Fresult would send a clear message that
OL,9,FDowning Street would struggle to
OL,10,Fignore.
OL,12,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
